text: #6ABCmessage Sorry if it feels like all the USA traveling is a big game of ping pong pontiff, Holy Father... but we're glad you're here! <3
@DomerAs @RMAofNY Followed! I'm a #redcup always willing to make friends. Thanks for dropping me a line!
@MissAmerica @AnnaKendrick47 @Pharrell ...just got told by a coffee cup & two champagne flutes that I'm not famous. It's true, but OUCH. :'(
#ImThankfulFor @MissAmerica, @AnnaKendrick47, & @Pharrell: without them, I'd never be famous! Hearts to you guys!! #Thanksgiving #redcup
My girl @MissAmerica is gonna be at the @6abcTDP to celebrate #Thanksgiving! Look close: you might see me on the float!! #redcup #6abcTDP
I'm still here... but there's nothing to tweet. Hanging out in the cupboard. No new gossip from the soup mugs or water glasses. #redcup
Hello, #America: I'm back! While I'll bet almost none of you missed me or my tweets, I missed you. It gets lonely in my cupboard. #redcup
“@WeLearnHistory: RT @oldpicsarchive: the first miss america contest, 1921 http://t.co/zz58G66ygH” Thought some1 had #redcup but it's a hat.
“@ThenVersusNow: Miss America contestants.. then and now. It's a great time to be alive, fellas http://t.co/ce4ha1MMZW” No #redcup for her.
@_RealShahid Well, hello to you, too!
@MissAmerica @reginahopper @GloriaAllred Way to rock the red dress, m'lady; don't suppose it's in honor of your #redcup pal? #WilsonSaysHi
I'd like to ask Mr. @paulfeig for a cameo in his #Ghostbusters remake. My #redcup self filled w/ green ooze, perhaps? Please? Maybe? #callme
“@AprilReynolds44: @missamericup @MissAmerica And what a great job she did!  But you deserve a big applause!” Aw, thanks!! #IdBlushButImRed
@AprilReynolds44 Well, gosh: thanks! It's nice to be noticed. I worked hard on my routine though @MissAmerica did the heavy lifting. #redcup
I remember #NYC. Bright lights, big city... me just a little red cup with somewhere to be. #redcup #NostalgicWilson http://t.co/MaHJJBgbA2
I feel so bewildered these days. Should I find my own path? Should I just hang out and play flip cup? Is that a thing? #redcup #missamerica
I don't think I miss being on a stage -- like during the #MissAmerica pageant -- but I do miss just getting out there & #dancing. #redcup
@PurpleRibbon: @MissAmerica This is National DV Awareness Month! I #GoPurple because... Even this #redcup wants less violence in the world.
This is my 100th tweet. Only 100 tweets but I have 47 followers!!!! That's amazing for just a #redcup like me. Remember #Wilson <3s you all!
Okay, world: what next? I'm over this cold & ready for action. I've danced & helped @MissAmerica & it's time to do something great! #redcup
“@linkedIn_agent: Miss America 2015: The Rumors Begin - WebProNews #linkedIn http://t.co/56sVQaU285” s'OK, I'm yesterday's news,too #redcup
Today, #MissAmerica went to a Chicago Bridal Market thing & saw nice gowns (I think). I sat in my cupboard. With a cold. #redcup #sadWilson
“@Rumi_Quote: Whatever purifies you is the right path.” Can someone tell that to the cold I still have? I'm a miserable #redcup here! :(
Now I'm resting up & looking for a new purpose while @MissAmerica has her epic reign! ...and is maybe too busy for me. #redcup #sadWilson
Having a cold & helping a flair bartender don't mix, btw. Sneezed & went flying into a row of bottles. They were nice about it but still. :(
@MissAmerica @Cosmopolitan Kira, we used to do these things together!! #DontYouForgetAboutMe #redcup #Wilson
RT @MissAmerica: Anyone who has seen Pitch Perfect will appreciate this video I did with @Cosmopolitan !! http://t.co/7zDuaN76fl
I did catch a cold. :( Now I'm wrapped up in a foam drink koozie -- think of it as the #redcup version of a Snuggie -- full of chicken soup.
@Truairmakeup @MissAmericaOrg Aw, yay! It's great to have someone to look up to and a dream to follow. #redcup https://t.co/CoBHMrCHpc
I still think I'm coming down with that cold. At least I know I can stay hydrated. Y'know, being a beverage container. #morecuphumor #redcup
Upside of being a #redcup when I'm on the beach -- or at the #shore, like you say in #AtlanticCity -- is I don't get sunburned! #cuphumor
@kathygriffin You looked nifty in your pageant sash on @LastWeekTonight! Just a humble cup sharing his opinion & wishing you well. #Wilson
@iamjohnoliver @LastWeekTonight Being a red plastic cup, I never got the scholarship side of pageantry before. Now I get it! Thanks! #redcup
Here's the @YouTube video for @LastWeekTonight with @iamjohnoliver: http://t.co/0MQKW0g0Lp  Scholarships are important; I learned a lot.
Wish @iamjohnoliver asked me to make a cameo on the #MissAmerica @LastWeekTonight ep! I admit, I LOL'd over the buttglue. #SorryKira #redcup
I think maybe I'm coming down with a cold or something. :( Wonder if that will turn me into a blue plastic cup. #redcup ...for now #Wilson
@redwhalecoffee That looks awesome! By the way, any job openings for durable & reusable red plastic cups with prior stage experience?
@RogerandJP @Pharrell Hey, there I am on stage! Neato! I haven't seen many good photos of me. They all seem to focus on Kira.
RT @PageantChris: 'I must've aged 10 years in the last 24 hours.' Go read Kira's blog and pray the girl can get some rest. http://t.co/oYQj…
“@_RealShahid: Who needs those snooty champagne glasses when you have @missamericup !!!” Thanks for that. At least I have friends here!
Gonna go dance to @Pharrell's Happy. Or watch #PitchPerfect. Or I'll see if @Pharrellhat wants to hang. #Bullies won't get me down. #redcup
That Collin guy didn't have to make fun of me; no one had to laugh. You never need to be made fun of for being you. #BullyingIsWrong #redcup
At flair bartending today, a Collins glass -- wiki it; I had to -- called me fat & laughed at me. A cocktail shaker laughed, too. #sad #hurt
When you fail... you pick yourself up, dust yourself off, & try again. Flair bartending gig attempt two, here I come! #redcup #GoWilsonGo
“@WNTonight: President Obama gives Marines the "Latte Salute": http://t.co/NX0ihPhmQQ” It would be my honor to salute our military. No joke.
Twitter asked me to follow @WheatThins. They're served on plates, in bowls, or their box. I'm a #redcup & don't eat. Ad fail? #PuzzledWilson
RT @Alpha_red1: Twitter is basically just you having a conversation with yourself hoping that someone else will join in other wise you feel…
BTW, flair bartending gig might not be for me: got tossed into the air, did a quad flip... fainted somewhere after that. #WilsonFail #redcup
Shoutout to one of the best followers a cup could have: @_RealShahid, dunno why you stick w/ my existential crises & randomness, but thanks!
@MissNevadaMAO Oh, Miss Nevada, it's such an honor: thx for the follow! Sorry if it felt like I never said hi backstage: I'm shy! #blushcup
Concerning press about  @KiraKazantsev or @MissAmericaOrg... I won't ever have any official comment. Why? I'm a tap-dancing plastic cup.
I've got it: Thanks to @MissAmerica, @Pharrell, and @AnnaKendrick47, I've got the right moves to partner up with a flair bartender! #redcup
Worried about the future. #MissAmerica's reign brings awareness, has importance. I don't, in that way. What can I do? #ExistentialCupCrisis
“@BEAUTIFULPlCS: Colors over Crater Lake, #Oregon. Photo by Shahid Durrani. http://t.co/honPamhuCm” I worry I'll never see beauty like this.
I can't be a performer forever but I'm not trained for anything else. I do NOT want to get stuck being a fast food container. Any job ideas?
Updated header photo: the pic of @MissAmerica posing w/ me in @TimesSquareNYC because that's a great memory. #Wilson & #Kira = #redcup #bffs
@silva1982 @MissAmerica Thanks for your support, Tony! Kira's working hard to be a great #MissAmerica ...but it's nice to be noticed, too!
The other day, I tried to strike up a conversation w/ a champagne flute who pretended I didn't exist. Kindness costs nothing. #bitch #redcup
Halloween costume idea number 2: get name tag & go as a @Target employee. I mean, I've got the uniform covered. #redcup #ThinkOutsideTheCup
Halloween costume idea number 1: some green & white makeup, a white hat... and I'd become a @Starbucks latte! What do you think? #redcup
@jimmyfallon Do you think you could write one of your great thank you notes for me tonight since I helped @missamerica win? Please? #redcup
“@WNTonight: Pope Francis' hat is up for auction on eBay - http://t.co/o0dV71DvdV” @MissAmerica Please don't auction me like this!!! #Wilson
@HeatherHabura Thanks for the follow! Maybe with your #pageant experience you could help me figure out some new #redcup dance moves?
RT @HeatherHabura: Courage is what it takes to stand up and speak; courage is also what it takes to sit down and listen. #lifequotes
Anyone think I should learn some dance moves to #RedSoloCup by @TobyKeithMusic? Sure, I'm not usually a 'solo' act... #morecuphumor #redcup
RT @GuardianLV_Ent: #MissAmerica Defends Her Plastic #RedCup Talent #RedCupTalent #GLV http://t.co/Ke1d35tu5z
Are you a pessimist or an optimist? Is the #redcup half empty or half full? #ISayHalfFull
@YvetteNY it was nice to meet you, too! @MissAmerica is the real star shining for the world to see but it's still great of you to notice me!
It's fun to be a part of the #MissAmerica experience, but I'm not the focus of her reign, okay? Domestic violence is no joke. #redcup
@YvetteNY @MissAmerica @MissAmericasCup @extratv @hm Hey, I'm right here! #bummed #leftout
@stoni_lin Well, you made a good point! I was awed by @chrisbharrison, but @TheEllenShow? I would've been so nervous to perform; she's epic!
@TamEdwards6abc Oh, re: being au courant... #MissAmerica contestants have to know their current events so I learned a lot. They're smart!
@TamEdwards6abc Aw, gosh: I'd blush if I wasn't already red. Thanks so much. #bashfulcup
@GMA @sesamestreet #GMASesameStreet Do you guys have any room for a hardworking cup? Never heard back from @AnnaKendrick47 or @Pharrell
RT @TamEdwards6abc: @missamericup oh red cup, there is no other like you and you are always au courant!
Honestly, it's not pleasant to get drummed upon, bonked on stage, or dragged over the floor. But I make it look good. #professional #redcup
A #MissAmerica post-pageant regret: I should've asked @chrisbharrison & his girlfriend @LeeMeriwether to sign me! #redcup
@missamericup By the way, the frat my brother is in? Alpha Cuppa Bru. Maybe? I think that's right. It's all Greek to me. #redcup #cuphumor
So does anyone have suggestions on how I should spend time in the next year? I think @MissAmerica is going to be too busy to sing w/ me. :(
RT @MissAmerica: Love this video of 2 little cuties that enjoyed my talent!! This is what #MissAmerica is all about!… http://t.co/w0s5Em58rU
“@_RealShahid: Ahahahahaha!! There she is @missamericup 😂😂😂😂 Wow guys!!!” I need to practice my pageant wave! ...oh, wait. No arms. #cupfail
My two favorite films are Pitch Perfect and The Brave Little Toaster. One taught me how to dance; the other taught me how to live. #bravecup
@accesshollywood @MissAmericaOrg @MissAmerica I'm proud of you, Kira! <3's from your talent sidekick. #redcup
My brother is in a fraternity. He's really good at beer pong. #redcup
@OTremell @DebbyeAtArise If not, let me offer my help! We'd be making music together in no time.
@kemrichardson7 Thanks so much for the follow! Starstruck to get noticed by a reporter like you; I'm just a humble cup helping @MissAmerica.
RT @kemrichardson7: @missamericup @ABC7NY watch at 5, fun! http://t.co/VXM1av8J27
I keep finding impostor cups claiming to be me. Their profile pics are those red solo cups. You all know I was in a double act! #cuphumor
When I was just a sippy cup, my mom told me to work hard and follow my dreams. #thanksmom #MissAmerica #redcup
@aliciavitarelli Wish I was a big talker on your news segment but I keep being referred to as a little red plastic cup. Not an ego boost.
@TamEdwards6abc Thanks for the follow! I might be yesterday's news but it's an honor for a cup like me to be noticed by an anchor like you.
@GMA I could totally be on @thechew! or GMA! You guys have to use cups for stuff all the time, right? I'm out of a job for the next year...
@TheEllenShow Maybe if you added a red plastic cup the song would be better? I'm free for the next year if you need help. #MissAmerica
It's so nice to have friends! I mean, I got to hang out backstage at #MissAmerica with the cosmetics, but having Twitter followers is great!
RT @_RealShahid: @missamericup you will go down in history as one of the most famous cups...besides The Holy Grail.
@_RealShahid Well, gosh, thanks! Hope I don't crack under the pressure. Glad I'm made of really sturdy plastic.
@matt_odonnell Thanks for the shout out, Matt! No one's asked me how I felt about our talent performance, so it's nice to be noticed.
@_RealShahid Thank you for the recognition! I'm not saying I'm as great as #MissAmerica or anything, but I was half of that talent act!
Wait: so I was an integral part of the talent routine but I don't get a mini-crown of my own? Not even a sash? #bummed #redcup #MissAmerica
@AnnaKendrick47 @Pharrell If either of you are ever looking to work with a moderately talented red plastic cup, drop me a line. #MissAmerica
When not practicing my talent, I like to hang out with the coffee mugs. They're nice. The wine glasses are divas. #MissAmerica #redcup
@GMA So proud of my girl Kira -- oops, I mean @MissAmerica now! I know not everyone liked our talent number but I tried my best!
@LaraSpencer Aw, I forgot to tell Kira that I really wanted my picture taken with you! #MissAmerica #sorrybucketlist #redcup
@peoplemag Actually, we're /both/ big fans of Pitch Perfect. I watched the film a lot to practice my talent.
@Newsday @MissAmerica I wouldn't say I'm a /little/ red cup... but yes. There's a lot going on in the world; I'm just a beverage container.
Lots of people are criticizing @MissAmerica for thumping me on the floor & warbling out her talent. Hm. I feel I worked hard, but... #redcup
@NormanJay3 @MissAmericaOrg @MissAmerica Physical beauty isn't the only thing that matters in life. Kindness matters much more.
@6abc It's nice to see that she's defending me. We worked hard on that routine!
@arobach @WNTonight @MissAmericaOrg @ABC How come no one has asked for an exclusive interview with Miss America's talented red cup sidekick?
@abcactionnews @MissAmerica I totally WAS happy, thanks for noticing! Oh. You meant the song. Well, yeah, that too. Still, it was fun!
@dailyherald Truth. I'm just a beverage container. There's real stuff going on in the world. But JSYK I worked hard on my performance!
@ABBQueenOfPeach @KiraKazantsev I would totally be down with beer pong as my new talent.
Congratulations on winning Miss Congeniality! #MissAmerica #2015MissAmerica
@MissOhio14 You and Roxy were amazing at the #MissAmerica pageant!
At least I didn't have to sing at the same time, even though they gave me a mike-pack. #2015MissAmerica #redcup #imnotagoodmultitasker
I was pretty nervous & totally missed my mark a few of times during the song. Did I do okay? #2015MissAmerica #redcup
Did anyone see me perform with @MissAmerica last night?! #redcup #2015MissAmerica #AtlanticCity
